---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { formatDate, getArticleCounts, getFeaturedArticles, getSectionLabel } from "../lib/articles";

const featured = getFeaturedArticles(6);
const [leadArticle, ...restArticles] = featured;
const counts = getArticleCounts();
---

<BaseLayout title="Yofinebook" description="中文技术写作与翻译，强调良好排版和安静阅读。">
  <section class="home-hero">
    <div class="hero-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Independent Reading Journal</p>
      <h1>把技术博客做成一页一页值得坐下来读的东西。</h1>
      <p class="hero-copy">
        这里不是信息流，也不是内容卡片堆叠。它更接近一本持续更新的阅读刊物，重视段落节奏、留白、标题层次和长时间停留时的舒适感。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-note">
      <p class="note-label">阅读取向</p>
      <p>偏长文，偏安静，偏适合晚上慢慢看。</p>
      <a href="/archive">进入归档</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="reading-metrics" aria-label="站点统计">
    <article>
      <span>{counts.total}</span>
      <p>当前文章总数</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>{counts.translations}</span>
      <p>翻译文章</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>{counts.posts}</span>
      <p>原创文章</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  {leadArticle && (
    <section class="feature-stage">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Latest Piece</p>
          <h2>最新主推</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/archive">查看全部</a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <a class="feature-lead" href={leadArticle.url}>
          <p class="eyebrow">{getSectionLabel(leadArticle.section)}</p>
          <h3>{leadArticle.title}</h3>
          <p>{leadArticle.summary}</p>
          <div class="meta-row">
            <span>{formatDate(leadArticle.date)}</span>
            <span>{leadArticle.readingMinutes} 分钟阅读</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <div class="feature-list">
          {restArticles.map((article) => (
            <a class="feature-item" href={article.url}>
              <div>
                <p class="eyebrow">{getSectionLabel(article.section)}</p>
                <h3>{article.title}</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-row">
                <span>{formatDate(article.date)}</span>
                <span>{article.readingMinutes} 分钟</span>
              </div>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <section class="editorial-strip">
    <article>
      <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
      <h2>不是追热点，而是做能反复回看的内容。</h2>
    </article>
    <article>
      <p class="eyebrow">Translation</p>
      <h2>翻译会尽量保留原文的结构和论证力度，而不是只摘结论。</h2>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="reading-promise">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Reading Experience</p>
      <h2>页面应该退到后面，让内容自己站到前面。</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
      因此这里刻意减少干扰式组件，强化标题层级、页内节奏和连续阅读路径。你点进一篇文章之后，应该感觉像是打开了一页被认真整理过的文本，而不是进入另一个内容容器。
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
